<div class="pbzh-chat-hdr"><div class="pbzh-chat-avatar"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 01-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 012-2h14a2 2 0 012 2z"/></svg></div><div class="pbzh-chat-info"><strong>PRINTIG.BZH</strong><span>Devis en moins de 48h</span></div><div class="pbzh-chat-status"><div class="pbzh-status-dot"></div><span class="pbzh-status-text">En ligne</span></div></div>
<div class="pbzh-chat-body" id="pbzh-body"></div>
<div class="pbzh-input-area">
<div class="pbzh-input-row">
